Description: Mystäre_is the original, must see Cirque du Soleil© show that combines powerful athleticism, high-energy acrobatics and inspiring imagery that has become the company_s hallmark.Deemed a theatrical "flower in the desert," Mystäre thrills generations of audiences with its exhilarating blend of whimsy, drama and the unimaginable brought to life on stage.Presented exclusively at Treasure Island, Mystäre provides the ultimate discovery that life itself is a mystery.Honored eight times as "Best Production Show" by the Las Vegas Review-Journal, Mystäre has an international cast of over 65 performers featuring dancers, singers, musicians and champion-caliber acrobats.
Location: 3300 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Marvel Avengers S.T.A.T.I.O.N. is an interactive and educational exhibit bringing visitors in the world of The Avengers.All ages are welcome to the official Scientific Training and Tactical Intelligence Operative Network (S.T.A.T.I.O.N.) headquarters, and dive deep into the Marvel Cinematic Universe.  Access exclusive intelligence files, classified studies, and experiments that explore the history and scientific origins of The Avengers while training to become an official agent of the S.T.A.T.I.O.N
Location: 3300 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
